features.title: Features
features.description: Flux AI Image Generator is a powerful tool that allows you to generate images from text prompts. It uses advanced AI models to create stunning images that are perfect for any project.

item1.title: FLUX.1 [pro]
item1.description: The best of FLUX.1, offering state-of-the-art performance image generation with top of the line prompt following, visual quality, image detail and output diversity.

item2.title: FLUX.1 [dev]
item2.description: Directly distilled from FLUX.1 [pro], FLUX.1 [dev] obtains similar quality and prompt adherence capabilities, while being more efficient than a standard model of the same size.

item3.title: FLUX.1 [schnell]
item3.description: The fastest image generation model tailored for local development and personal use

item4.title: Lightning-Fast
item4.description: Flux AI generates high-quality images in seconds, significantly faster than Stable Diffusion 3 and Midjourney. With its lightning-fast image generation capabilities, Flux AI ensures quick and efficient results, saving you valuable time and resources.

item5.title: Customizable
item5.description: The advanced Flux.1 model produces more detailed and coherent images than competitors. With its customizable features and user-friendly interface, Flux AI Image Generator is the ultimate tool for generating stunning images from text prompts. Whether you're a beginner or a professional, Flux AI has got you covered. Experience the power of AI and revolutionize your image generation process today!

item6.title: User-Friendly Interface
item6.description: Easier to use than ComfyUI, perfect for beginners and pros alike. Flux AI Image Generator is the ultimate tool for generating stunning images from text prompts. With its user-friendly interface and powerful AI models, Flux AI makes it easy for both beginners and professionals to create amazing visuals.

faq.subtitle: Explore our comprehensive FAQ to find quick answers to common inquiries. If you need further assistance, don't hesitate to contact us for personalized help.

item1.question: How does Flux AI compare to Stable Diffusion 3?
item1.answer: Flux AI offers faster generation times, higher image quality, and a more user-friendly interface compared to Stable Diffusion 3. The Flux.1 model incorporates the latest advancements in AI research.

item2.question: Is Flux AI available on GitHub or Hugging Face?
item2.answer: Yes, Flux AI is open-source and available on both GitHub and Hugging Face.

item3.question: What makes Flux AI different from other AI image generators?
item3.answer: Flux AI combines speed, quality, and ease of use. It's faster than Midjourney, more user-friendly than ComfyUI, and produces higher quality images than many competitors.

item4.question: How to use Flux AI?
item4.answer: To use Flux AI, simply visit fluxaipro.art, enter your prompt, and witness the creation of breathtaking visuals in a matter of seconds.

item5.question: What pricing plans does Flux AI offer?
item5.answer: We use points to use our services, and you can click on the price card to buy points (only one payment is required).

item6.question: How can I get support for Online?
item6.answer: You can reach out to us at support@douni.one.
